snippet.title: Heroes of Hammerwatch, Pyramid of Prophecy, Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Pyramid of Prophecy is the expansion/dlc that brings you all new content to Heroes of Hammerwatch, with a new campaign, class, gameplay-features, and much more.

http://www.heroesofhammerwatch.com

Game is available on Steam and Gog.

http://store.steampowered.com/app/677120/Heroes_of_Hammerwatch/

https://www.gog.com/game/heroes_of_hammerwatch

Crackshell Twitter for faster updates: https://twitter.com/RealCrackshell
